data.description: Welcome home! This split level 3 bed/2 bath contemporary offers privacy and nature views from almost every window. Enjoy the serene private views from the screened porch overlooking the fenced backyard, or relax in the comfortable family room with vaulted ceiling and gorgeous woodwork.Features include: New engineered wood flooring in main living areas, New primary bathroom (full Renovation) with beautiful tiled shower/dual copper sinks/custom cabinetry, New kitchen with custom cabinets/granite countertops/bar seating, New light fixtures, Fresh exterior & interior paint, New garage doors, New sliding doors to back porch, New water heater, New grinder pump, Roof 2017. Such a unique and special home with character!
